Package: pharmsolr
Title: R Bindings for pharmsol JIT-Compiled PK Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("pharmsol", "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Defines a pharmacometric model in plain text, JIT-compiles it via
    Cranelift through the 'pharmsol' Rust crate, and runs simulations from R
    without invoking 'cargo' or 'rustc' on every call. Built once, the package
    runs any model definition at runtime.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
